Title: Introduction to C Programming
Details: Learn the fundamentals of programming using the C language.This course covers variables, data types, control structures, functions, arrays, pointers, and basic file handling.

Title: Introduction to Algorithms
Details: Explore fundamental algorithms and data structures. Learn how to analyze and design efficient algorithms for a variety of computational problems.

Title: Introduction to C++ for DSA
Details: Master the basics of C++ programming and learn how to implement fundamental data structures and algorithms it will be distracted by the readable content

Title: Basic Data Structures
Details: Learn the fundamental data structures used in computer science, including arrays, linked lists, stacks, queues, and basic algorithms for manipulating them.

Title: Introduction to OOP Python
Details: Learn the principles of object-oriented programming using Python. Understand classes, objects, inheritance, polymorphism, and how to apply them in practical programming projects.

Title: Software Engineering
Details: Learn the principles and best practices of software engineering. Covering requirements analysis, design, coding, testing, and maintenance of software systems.

Title: AWS, Cloud Computing
Details: Master the fundamentals of cloud computing and learn how to deploy, manage, and scale applications on Amazon Web Services (AWS) platform.

Title: Database (MySQL)
Details: Learn the fundamentals of database management using MySQL. Covering topics from designing databases to writing complex queries and database administration.

Title: Problem-Solving Part
Details: Enhance your problem-solving skills through a series of challenging exercises. Learn various techniques and strategies to approach complex problems.
